project_name: secured_mqtt
label: secured_mqtt
description: >
  This example project demonstrates how to run a secured MQTT application with the Wi-Fi FMAC driver, the LwIP functionalities and the MbedTLS library.
category: Example|Platform
package: platform
quality: evaluation
